node.text:
How can a dream come true? Through an immense passion and an enormous commitment. It is through this vision that Enzo Ferrari has built one of the most iconic brands the world has ever seen. A vision that always puts excellence and quality first, infused in all the people that have crossed the threshold of the gates of Maranello, working to preserve its legacy.⁣
On this day, 33 years after his passing, we are #RememberingEnzo.
